        "effect": {
          "before": "<p>Dreyfus transforms into a new form. Each form grants a secondary attack he can use as a maneuver this turn:</p><ul><li><strong>Dire Wolf Form:</strong> Pack Lunge — Melee, Agility vs Might; 11 damage, target is prone.</li><li><strong>Raven Form:</strong> Wyrd-Shriek — Close Burst 2, Intuition vs Intuition; 5 damage, all targets dazed until end of next turn. Speed becomes 10 (flying).</li><li><strong>Shadow Form:</strong> Drain Warmth — Ranged touch, Presence vs Presence; 8 cold damage, target loses 1 Recovery.</li></ul><p>At 20 Stamina or below, Dreyfus can no longer maintain animal shapes and reverts to humanoid form permanently.</p>",
