      "_id": "DREY200000000006",
      "name": "Shape Collapse",
      "type": "feature",
      "img": "icons/magic/unholy/orb-glowing-yellow-purple.webp",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>When reduced to 0 Stamina, Dreyfus does not die. He collapses into a pool of shadow and is incapacitated. He cannot reform. He is finished — not destroyed, but ended as an agent. For one moment, he looks completely human — not a shape-walker, but a person who has been doing something terrible for a very long time and has finally been stopped.</p>",
          "director": ""
        },
